<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.1.2">
<l>yāvarumā yāvaiyumā yeḻilvētap poruḷkaḷumāy</l>
<l>mūvarumāy mutalāya mūrttiyamarn tuṟaiyumiṭam</l>
<l>māvarumtiṇ paṭaimaṉṉai veṉṟikoḷvārmaṉṉunāṅkai</l>
<l>tēvarumceṉ ṟiṟaiñcupoḻil tiruttēva ṉārtokaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place where serenely dwells the embodiment as the cause,</l>
<l rend="indent">as the Three,</l>
<l>As the meaning of the beautiful Vedas, as all things and as all people,</l>
<l>Is Tiruttēvaṉārtokai in the grove where gods go and bow</l>
<l>In Nāṅkai where stay those who gain victory [over] kings</l>
<l rend="indent">with strong weapons who come on horses.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
